OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,FThe SNP has called on Andy Burnham to
OL,7,Fdeliver an emergency cost-of-living
OL,8,Fbudget to "reverse damage" under the
OL,9,FLabour Government.
OL,11,FMr Burnham is set to become prime
OL,12,Fminister on Monday after he was
OL,13,Fconfirmed as Labour leader on Friday.
OL,15,FThe former Greater Manchester mayor,
OL,16,Fwho returned to Westminster last month
OL,17,Fas the MP for Makerfield, vowed to
OL,18,F"bring back hope" in his speech as
OL,19,FLabour leader on Friday.
OL,26,@pD@KOUpD@ZO]zD@AOUzD@QO]
