OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,FSNP Westminster leader Dave Doogan
OL,7,Fsaid that Mr Burnham would be "judged
OL,8,Fon his actions not words" as the UK
OL,9,Fprepares for its seventh prime
OL,10,Fminister in 10 years.
OL,12,FMr Doogan is calling on Mr Burnham to
OL,13,Fdeliver an emergency cost-of-living
OL,14,Fbudget when he enters No 10.
OL,16,FHe continued: "While Westminster has
OL,17,Fbeen stuck in constant chaos, people's
OL,18,Flives have got worse.
OL,26,@oD@_OUpD@YO]xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
