OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784517496
OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,F"People in Scotland don't want more
OL,7,Fempty promises about 'hope in their
OL,8,Fhearts' ` they want money in their
OL,9,Fpockets and meaningful change to make
OL,10,Fpeople's lives and livelihoods better.
OL,12,F"Andy Burnham must deliver an
OL,13,Femergency cost of living budget, and a
OL,14,Fmeaningful package of financial
OL,15,Fsupport for families, to reverse the
OL,16,Fdamage done under the Labour Party
OL,17,Fgovernment and put money back into
OL,18,Fpeople's pockets.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
