OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,F"That must include tackling the
OL,7,Fsoaring cost of energy bills, which
OL,8,Fare almost #600 higher than the Labour
OL,9,FParty promised at the election,
OL,10,Freducing the sky-high cost of fuel,
OL,11,Fand reversing the billions of pounds
OL,12,Fof damage done to Scottish jobs,
OL,13,Fbusinesses and the economy by the
OL,14,FLabour Party's National Insurance tax
OL,15,Fhike and harmful Brexit policies.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
