SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1784517496
OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,F"It means changing the damaging
OL,7,Fapproach to Scottish industry, which
OL,8,Fhas seen the Labour government
OL,9,Fshutting the doors on Grangemouth,
OL,10,Fdestroying thousands of Scottish
OL,11,Fenergy jobs and hoarding Scotland's
OL,12,Fenergy wealth at Westminster."
OL,14,FIn his pitch for the Labour
OL,15,Fleadership, Mr Burnham focused on
OL,16,Fdevolution and said he wanted to
OL,17,Fdecentralise Westminster, including an
OL,18,Fextension of the prime minister's
OL,19,Foffice in Manchester dubbed "No 10
OL,20,FNorth".
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@^O]{D@]OU|D@FO]
