OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney said he
OL,7,Fwill be meeting the incoming prime
OL,8,Fminister next week and said that if Mr
OL,9,FBurnham "is serious about a genuinely
OL,10,Fnew approach", the SNP will be a
OL,11,F"willing partner".
OL,13,FHowever, he said the new prime
OL,14,Fminister must recognise Westminster
OL,15,F"does not have the right to dictate
OL,16,FScotland's future" as he pushes for
OL,17,Fanother independence referendum.
OL,19,FIt has already been reported that Mr
OL,20,FBurnham would likely oppose such a
OL,21,Fvote.
OL,26,@qD@IOUrD@MO]sD@AOUsD@QO]wD@AOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
