OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,FMr Doogan said that Mr Burnham must
OL,7,Fbring a "radical change approach" to
OL,8,FScotland's parliament and democracy.
OL,10,FHe said: "And a new prime minister
OL,11,Fmust mean a radical change in approach
OL,12,Fto Scotland's parliament and democracy
OL,13,F` ditching Westminster's disrespect
OL,14,Fagenda, strengthening the powers of
OL,15,Fthe Scottish Parliament, and
OL,16,Frespecting Scotland's democratic right
OL,17,Fto determine our own future in an
OL,18,Findependence referendum.
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@aO]rD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
