OL,3,CAndy Burnham must deliver emergency
OL,4,Cbudget to 'reverse damage', says SNP
OL,6,F"The SNP is ready to work with a new
OL,7,Fprime minister to secure real support
OL,8,Fwith the cost of living and meaningful
OL,9,Fchange but that must include genuine
OL,10,Frespect for Scotland."
OL,12,FLabour has been approached for comment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@VO]
